781
00:34:37.320 --> 00:34:41.199
He makes a desperate attempt
to escape but is caught.

782
00:34:41.320 --> 00:34:44.600
On January 17. 1961.
Lumumba is recaptured

783
00:34:44.719 --> 00:34:48.880
and flown into Katanga
