00:34:52.400 --> 00:34:54.120
drive him out into the bush

786
00:34:54.239 --> 00:34:57.680
where he's executed on the spot.

787
00:34:57.800 --> 00:35:00.840
Patrice Lumumba.
the first democratically

788
00:35:00.960 --> 00:35:03.400
elected prime minister
of an independent Congo.

789
00:35:03.520 --> 00:35:05.640
is dead at 35.

790
00:35:05.760 --> 00:35:10.080
In his place. the CIA's
strongman. Colonel Mobutu.

791
00:35:10.200 --> 00:35:12.560
rules the Congo for over three decades.

792
00:35:12.680 --> 00:35:14.880
But piece by piece. the CIA's role

793
00:35:15.000 --> 00:35:18.040
in this rogue assassination is uncovered.

794
00:35:18.160 --> 00:35:20.960
The story first comes to light in 1975.

795
00:35:21.080 --> 00:35:24.400
when Congress investigates
the CIA's illicit activities.

796
00:35:24.520 --> 00:35:26.360
Then. in 2021. a British author

797
00:35:26.480 --> 00:35:28.600
named Susan Williams stitches details

798
00:35:28.720 --> 00:35:30.560
from newly declassified documents.

799
00:35:30.680 --> 00:35:33.200
and she uncovers what she
