851
00:37:59.160 --> 00:38:01.280
He just wants to disrupt
the Civil Rights movement.

852
00:38:01.400 --> 00:38:03.560
As Hoover digs into
Martin Luther King Jr..

853
00:38:03.680 --> 00:38:06.000
he bugs his hotel room. taps his phones.

854
00:38:06.120 --> 00:38:08.200
puts him under 24-hour surveillance.

855
00:38:08.320 --> 00:38:09.880
all without warrants from the courts.

856
00:38:10.000 --> 00:38:11.760
Eventually. they record evidence.

857
00:38:11.880 --> 00:38:13.520
Not that King is a Communist.

858
00:38:13.640 --> 00:38:16.200
but that he's been having an affair.

859
00:38:16.320 --> 00:38:18.120
It's the ammunition Hoover needs

860
00:38:18.240 --> 00:38:20.120
