861
00:38:20.240 --> 00:38:23.640
Now COINTELPRO crosses
the biggest line yet.

862
00:38:23.760 --> 00:38:26.600
In November of 1964.
King receives a package.

863
00:38:26.720 --> 00:38:29.800
Inside are audio recordings documenting

864
00:38:29.920 --> 00:38:31.920
