865
00:38:32.040 --> 00:38:34.040
There's also an anonymous
threatening letter.

866
00:38:34.160 --> 00:38:36.560
He calls King a fraud and tells him.

867
00:38:36.680 --> 00:38:38.600
"There is but one way out for you."

868
00:38:38.720 --> 00:38:42.920
The FBI seems to be telling
a Nobel Peace Prize winner

869
00:38:43.040 --> 00:38:44.280
to kill himself.

870
00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:45.600
It's not subtle.

871
00:38:45.720 --> 00:38:47.480
King refuses.

872
00:38:47.600 --> 00:38:50.880
Hoover's unchecked operation
targets citizens across America

873
00:38:51.000 --> 00:38:52.440
