882
00:39:18.680 --> 00:39:20.160
immoral. and unethical.

883
00:39:20.280 --> 00:39:22.000
Their plan?

884
00:39:22.120 --> 00:39:24.760
Break into an FBI office to
steal documents that prove it.

885
00:39:24.880 --> 00:39:26.840
Their target is a lightly guarded

886
00:39:26.960 --> 00:39:28.920
field office in Pennsylvania.

887
00:39:29.040 --> 00:39:32.520
And they'll do it on
the perfect night for a heist.

888
00:39:32.640 --> 00:39:36.560
On March 8. 1971.
Muhammad Ali and Joe Frazier

889
00:39:36.680 --> 00:39:39.200
are gearing up
for the fight of the century.

890
00:39:39.320 --> 00:39:42.240
Millions of Americans.
including local police.

891
00:39:42.360 --> 00:39:44.400
are gonna be glued to their televisions.

892
00:39:44.520 --> 00:39:47.000
Dressed in suits and evening wear.

893
00:39:47.120 --> 00:39:48.760
the team approaches the office as if

894
00:39:48.880 --> 00:39:51.000
they're heading to a party. They break in.

895
00:39:51.120 --> 00:39:53.840
And once inside. they ignore
