922
00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:01.440
Determined to find the burglars.

923
00:41:01.560 --> 00:41:04.320
he unleashes 200 agents.
one of the largest

924
00:41:04.440 --> 00:41:06.960
manhunts in FBI history.

925
00:41:07.080 --> 00:41:09.400
For 40 years.
the identities of the burglars

926
00:41:09.520 --> 00:41:12.160
